title: Uphill Jeep Driver
fullContent: Home› DrivingUphill Jeep DriverBy OnlineGames.ioMake Game Full ScreenDriving a jeep over a hill full of obstacles was never as fun as in Uphill Jeep Driver game. Enjoy the landspaces while you drive the passengers carefully to the destination.  On the road you might meet a lot of obstacles like winding trails and broken cars. You will become a good driver when you pass the dangerous levels and keep your car far from falling down the cliff. Good luck completing all the 10 missions!Uphill Jeep Driver Controls:• WASD to control jeep• C to change camera• Escape to pauseThis article was updated on January 15, 20241 Player3DCarDrivingFreeTraffic
